oncrm.com/Articles/CRM-News/Daily-News/Socialbakers-Adds-New-Features-to-Social-Media-Management-System-85173.aspx|title=Socialbakers Adds New Features to Social Media Management System|accessdate=17 October 2012|publisher=Destination CRM|archive-date=2016-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160829063500/http://www.destinationcrm.com/Articles/CRM-News/Daily-News/Socialbakers-Adds-New-Features-to-Social-Media-Management-System-85173.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>

